Company Overview of Old West Investment Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Old West Investment Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals and pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to individuals, institutions, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, balanced, and alternative asset portfolios. It also launches and manages hedge funds. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets of United States. For its equity portfolios, it invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap and SMID-cap companies. For its alternative asset portfolios, the firm employs long/short and...
Old West Investment Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals and pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to individuals, institutions, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, balanced, and alternative asset portfolios. It also launches and manages hedge funds. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets of United States. For its equity portfolios, it invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap and SMID-cap companies. For its alternative asset portfolios, the firm employs long/short and absolute return strategies to make its investments. It employs fundamental analysis to make its investments. The firm benchmarks its equity portfolios against the Russell 1000, Russell 2500, and S&P 500 Index. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. Old West Investment Management, LLC was founded in 2008 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
Detailed Description


